summary: A small beginning cottage for a player to rest in. North of Solitude on the coast
descriptionHtml:
A small beginning cottage for a player to rest in. North of Solitude on the coast, no quest is required for access. Its a small cottage designed for the player in early stages of the game or one who has a thing for living humble. The reason its dwarven is just for pure personal taste of mine.

What it Has
________________
Anvil
Tanner
Workbench
Grindstone
Cooking Spit
Arcane Enchanter
A few Chests
One Bed
author: Rotsi
